and 
<collectingRegion id="0650F81CFFCC6A73FC5593DF1A6DBE95" box="[937,1133,1414,1447]" country="Philippines" name="Davao del Sur" pageId="55" pageNumber="813">Davao del Sur</collectingRegion>
provinces on Mindanao I), Borneo (Crocker Range in 
<collectingRegion id="0650F81CFFCC6A73FAFF93E81D0FBEC4" country="Malaysia" name="Sabah" pageId="55" pageNumber="813">Sabah</collectingRegion>
